This application uses content under the terms of CC BY-SA 4.0.

Attribution: Content is authored by Wiktionary contributors. Per the license,
the source of each entry is the English Wiktionary (https://en.wiktionary.org/).
Individual entry revision histories serve as the record of authorship.

Modifications: Raw wikitext markup is parsed and transformed into structured
data (JSON). Definitions, pronunciations, and labels are extracted; formatting,
examples, quotations, translations, and other non-essential content is removed.
